subject: Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Most Nextel Cup drivers will tell you that racing at Daytona and Talladega — Nascar's two longest and fastest ovals — with carburetor restrictor plates, is not their favorite thing.
